cells.name: Instructions
cells.note:
Use Template Variables to configure this dashboard.

`:SalIndex:` tells you to use the Camera (1) or the M2 (2) Hexapod.

Use `:sampling:` to adjust the sampling interval, the default is High Performance which means let Chronograf adjust the `:interval:` variable for you.
